sg":"咁都有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd314f4d70d72589509a31a74317164ed9cbb775","tid":2451753,"uid":283240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90bb23b0797f12119f380481b9afff7a502b5195","tid":2451753,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae55362d316931dd7f4c3e8c91b48a0fe164d502","tid":2451753,"uid":283240,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed93809c67a0b6b0e3522627f73b777a3dda8f01","tid":2451753,"uid":69913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"剩係知最靚既資產係哂1113<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"好pk 小股東一定唔可以俾老隻老狐狸得逞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"咁都有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T17:04:39.000Z","msg":"連燈仔弱智廢青唔係第一日"},{"pid":"151e447616a61a59e2de327de6296c33bd20e898","tid":2451753,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"唔明，增發再回購，咁如果無人賣股俾佢咪回購唔到囉，如果佢自己賣返d新股出去，咁同現金收購有乜分別？係咪為咗避稅？"},{"pid":"a63ed4da2d656f8303eea4024c6028feb89e1ef1","tid":2451753,"uid":205303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca4c0105fb2dcbd8e5dc4a7ffc15adcbbc4b323d","tid":2451753,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210318/4HNIDFOPGNAOXPWEELJOPQIKFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210318%2F4HNIDFOPGNAOXPWEELJOPQIKFM%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2Ysqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=2eceb521\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210318%2F4HNIDFOPGNAOXPWEELJOPQIKFM%2F&h=7b3635a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210318/4HNIDFOPGNAOXPWEELJOPQIKFM/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"小粉紅經常叫「別讓超人跑了」，但事實係，「超人跑了而你不知道」。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠父子今次藉收購資產回購操作，增加長實達9個百分點股權，相當於五年自己在場內慢慢增持的比重。李氏放棄揼石仔，急於短時間內增持，李澤鉅在視象會議上補充：「簡單嚟講，股價會靚仔啲」。近數年持有長和系的股東，對李澤鉅這句說話，一定嗤之以鼻。李澤鉅不在乎股價，只在乎最後結果，與其相信他們覺得股價被估值，要釋放股東價值，我更相信是李氏父子鋪路私有化、為另一次世紀重紀揭開序幕。<br />\n<br />\n長和系一直為人所詬病，是其資產分散，定位不清。簡單一項英國電廠，長建、電能，甚至基金會都有份，轉讓予長實後，只是過渡性質。一直以來，很多人仍認為香港仍是長實盈利最大地區，但按地區區分，長實去年內地收入284億元，佔整體741億元的38%。而長實最值錢的，是其內地土地儲備資產。就算近年不斷賣走內地物業，長實可開發土地儲備仍有8,000萬呎，香港佔500萬呎、海外佔400萬呎，其餘7,100萬呎(佔88%)卻位於內地。<br />\n<br />\n作為上市公司，每一次賣走內地資產，沽售大型項目，少不免被外界冠以走資稱號。截至去年底，長實資產淨值為3,672億元，遠高於目前市值1,738億元。在政治越趨敏感環境下，如何走資賣產卻毋須露暴在閃光燈下，趁股價低水時收集股權、然後等待合適時機私有化，這更符合李澤鉅計到盡的風格。"},{"pid":"904d95e5d6abde3bc73ddcee520cfc119ecdf031","tid":2451753,"uid":208940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T19:13:45.000Z","msg":"大把誠哥老股民fans係70幾蚊買架，<br />\n大仔$51就想私有化，棺材本都蝕埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩兄弟一樣，當年8號仔老股民收息股，被煎皮拆骨"},{"pid":"c75216bfcbf3c2be88908cd5f56ba361027a2758","tid":2451753,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f1809489ea8383c91937f5e27dd013cbe0d35c","tid":2451753,"uid":133534,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:05:27.000Z","msg":"想賺誠哥錢 好難啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T19:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做長實股東不知幾好<br />\n曾經"},{"pid":"d97dfafffb504e66a55dac0d5e655fe5b7d4e124","tid":2451753,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T19:29:48.000Z","msg":"執靚長實賣咗佢之後私有化長和<br />\n鳩估"},{"pid":"320c4da630333f34a15e582466397780a9242a91","tid":2451753,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"904d95e5d6abde3bc73ddcee